title: 649 Picnic Time Metro Melrose
description: When a traditional picnic basket seems too formal, the Melrose - Moka by Picnic Time is just what you're looking for. It's made of durable 600D polyester in dark brown with an accent of Moka stripes, and has an aluminum frame to make it lightweight, yet sturdy. The Melrose - Moka has picnic service for four and features a water-resistant interior and expandable, drawstring top.

transcripts: When a traditional picnic basket seems too formal, the Metro Melrose by Picnic Time is just what you need. Made of durable polyester on an aluminum frame, the Melrose is lightweight yet sturdy. It includes picnic service for four and features a water resistant interior for the convenient drawstring top. Unzip the front exterior pocket and all of it's amenities are are your disposal including tumblers, napkins, flatware and plate. Thermoguard high density foam insulation keeps your food and drinks cool for hours and the expandable drawstrip top can accommodate a very large picnic. With the Melrose, your picnic awaits.
